body: This is an amazing doujin the only bad thing about it is that it only is nine pages, give me 30 more and this will be easily top tier. the artwork and story are smooth as hell leading right after the daihasei festival. I need more fukiyose seiri doujins but like misaki is overshadowed by misaka, maybe thats a good thing, ah hell I don't even know anymore. 8/10
